1-JSON data -

 Json data is in the form of string
we can get random json data from apis such as https://catfact.ninja/fact
we can validate the Json data using online json validators and know more about json data using json.org

2-Accessing Data in JSon-
Json data comes in the form of string so we use Json.parse to parse string to js object

let JsonRes='{"fact":"Neutering a cat extends its life span by two or three years.","length":60}'
let validdata=jSon.parse(JsonRes);

in this jSon.parse we are converting json data to object

json.stringify(json)-parse a json object to json

Testing Api request- HOppscoth and postman


3-AJAX- Asynchronous Javascript and XML
    This is the process through which we send APi calls and recieve response which is a an asynchrounous process
    jis bhi api ko ham req bhejenge to kuch response ata hai kuch saal phle jo response tha vo xml mai aya karta tha
    ab ham xml use nahi karte par kyuki kafi time se ajax nam hogya to vhai bolte hai lekin use json hi hota hai

4- Status code
    200-ok
    404-api not found
    400- bad request
    500- internal server error
    